summary: Completed all Beauty Booking module frontend tasks: (1) Added separate clinic dashboard with conditional rendering based on business_type, showing clinic-specific statistics (patients, visits) vs salon statistics. (2) Created React search page (SalonSearchPage.jsx) for public salon/clinic listing with filters, pagination, and Material-UI components. (3) Implemented complete rating system frontend with RatingDisplay, ReviewCard, ReviewModal, and SalonReviews React components. (4) Added revenue models breakdown display in vendor dashboard showing all 10 revenue streams. (5) Set up Laravel Mix build process with webpack.mix.js and package.json for React components compilation. All components are integrated with existing Blade templates and API endpoints.
